{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/reduce-repetition-using-the-repeat-function","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"css-grid","demoType":null,"title":"Smanji ponavljanje korišćenjem funkcije za ponavljanje","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Koristili ste <code>grid-template-columns</code> i <code>grid-template-rows</code> za kreiranje mrežne strukture, uneli ste vrednosti za svaki red ili stub koji ste kreirali.</p>\n<p>Recimo da želite mrežu sa 100 redova jednakih visina. Nije baš lako unositi vrednost 100 jednu po jednu. Srećom, postoji bolji način – korišćenjem funkcije <code>repeat</code> koja pokazuje koliko puta želite da se ponovi red ili kolona, praćen zarezom i vrednošću koju želite da ponovite.</p>\n<p>Evo primera koji bi kreirao mrežu od 100 redova, pri čemu svaki red ima visinu od 50px.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">grid-template-rows: repeat(100, 50px);\n</code></pre>\n<p>Takođe možete ponoviti više vrednosti korišćenjem funkcije „repeat“ i ubaciti tu funkciju između drugih vrednosti prilikom kreiranja mrežnog uzorka. To izgleda ovako:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr 50px) 20px;\n</code></pre>\n<p>Hii inatafsiriwa kama:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">grid-template-columns: 1fr 50px 1fr 50px 20px;\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>Napomena:</strong> <code>1fr 50px</code> se ponavlja dva puta, a zatim sledi <code>20px</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"5a94fe3669fb03452672e45f","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Koristi <code>repeat</code> da ukloni duplikate iz atributa <code>grid-template-columns</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/p/pByETK/cQvqyHR","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301133,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/reduce-repetition-using-the-repeat-function"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\n  .item1 {\n    background: LightSkyBlue;\n  }\n  .item2 {\n    background: LightSalmon;\n  }\n  .item3 {\n    background: PaleTurquoise;\n  }\n  .item4 {\n    background: LightPink;\n  }\n  .item5 {\n    background: PaleGreen;\n  }\n\n  .container {\n    font-size: 40px;\n    min-height: 300px;\n    width: 100%;\n    background: LightGray;\n    display: grid;\n    /* Only change code below this line */\n\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\n\n    /* Only change code above this line */\n    grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\n    grid-gap: 10px;\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"container\">\n  <div class=\"item1\">1</div>\n  <div class=\"item2\">2</div>\n  <div class=\"item3\">3</div>\n  <div class=\"item4\">4</div>\n  <div class=\"item5\">5</div>\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Klasa <code>container</code> mora imati svojstvo <code>grid-template-columns</code> koje je podešeno za ponavljanje u redovima 3 sa širinom od <code>1fr</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(\n  code,\n  /.container\\s*?{[\\s\\S]*grid-template-columns\\s*?:\\s*?repeat\\s*?\\(\\s*?3\\s*?,\\s*?1fr\\s*?\\)\\s*?;[\\s\\S]*}/gi\n);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#css-grid","dashedName":"reduce-repetition-using-the-repeat-function","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"css-grid","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/limit-item-size-using-the-minmax-function","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/use-grid-area-without-creating-an-areas-template","id":"5a94fe3669fb03452672e45f","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>\r\n  .item3 {\r\n    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;\r\n    display: grid;\r\n  }\r\n</style>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/reduce-repetition-using-the-repeat-function"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}